<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比在黑暗的隧道里陪着男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蜡烛快要烧完了。男孩儿终于醒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，你醒了！太棒了！”鲍比说，“别再晕倒了！你叫什么名字？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吉姆。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫鲍比。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比不是男孩儿的名字吗？”男孩儿问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。我真正的名字叫洛波塔。但是我希望自己是个男孩儿。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的弟弟和妹妹去找人帮忙了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么没有跟他们一起去？”吉姆问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为需要有人陪着你。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比，你真勇敢！”吉姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蜡烛烧完了。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比 ，你怕黑吗？”吉姆问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是很怕。”鲍比说，“但是……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们拉着手吧。”吉姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把自己的大手放在鲍比的小手上。他们坐着继续等。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得和菲利斯跑到一个农场里求助。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们和农夫们一起到达时，发现鲍比和吉姆都已经睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫们把吉姆抬到一块木板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他住在哪里？”一个农夫问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在诺森伯兰。”鲍比回答，“他刚才告诉我的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可以先把他送到我们家，离这儿不远。妈妈一定会同意的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈确实同意了，虽然她有一点惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很抱歉，给您添麻烦了。”被抬进房间时，吉姆对妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的脸还是很苍白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，医生很快就来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈还给吉姆的学校写了一封信，把所有事情告诉了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我爷爷住在附近。”吉姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会写信告诉他的。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 第二天，有人敲门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“应该是医生来了。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不是医生，可是他的声音很耳熟。会是谁呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，妈妈大喊：“吉姆的爷爷来了。他想见你们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们跟着妈妈来到前厅，是……老先生！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，是您！”鲍比说。孩子们看到老爷爷都很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您不会要带吉姆走吧？我希望他能多待一段时间。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老先生笑了。“我不带他走。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们的妈妈很善良。吉姆会留下来，她会好好儿照顾他的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “那妈妈怎么写故事呢？”彼得问。没人来得及阻止他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 老先生对妈妈笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “她可以不用写故事了，你们会有足够的食物。”老先生说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “鲍比，你可以送我到门口吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 老先生和鲍比走到门外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比，我收到了你的信，其实在收到你的信之前，我已经看过报纸了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我也试过帮助他。我能做的虽然不多，但还是有希望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “天呐！”鲍比激动地要哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “但是你要继续保密。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “您也觉得不是爸爸做的，对吗？”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我很确定不是他做的。”老先生说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>